	<h1 class="title">据说去年这些游戏最会讲故事，不过玩家们还想到了别的</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/57300/small/57300.jpg?1427187252" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">唐舒畅 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-01-12 19:18:22 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/20593/medium/20593.jpg?1452576159" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="20593" data-title="《据说去年这些游戏最会讲故事，不过玩家们还想到了别的》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/20593/medium/20593.jpg?1452576159" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/20593.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
